timeline.bodyText:
How about moving the creation into a new private method:
   final PrivacyController privacyController = privacyController()
    ...
}

private PrivacyController privacyController(){
    return privacyParameters.isMultiTenancyEnabled()
             ? new MultiTenancyPrivacyController(
                 defaultPrivacyController, privacyParameters.getEnclave())
             : new DefaultPrivacyController(
             privacyParameters, protocolSchedule.getChainId(), markerTransactionFactory);;
}

Besides making the create methods short & nicer to read, as a bonus It'll only create the default controller when it is needed.

